prompts.frontCover: A whimsical watercolor illustration of a charmingly disgruntled cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat. The sloth is hanging upside down from a tree branch, looking utterly unimpressed, while a cheerful bluebird places a single lit candle on its belly. Below the sloth, the text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, handwritten cursive script. The scene is rendered in soft, flowing watercolor style with visible artistic brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture, creating a lighthearted and funny 2D artwork.
